SUPERMAN
    MAX ALL STATS - Here it is, the quick and easy way to make Superman
                    for your party.

    Here are the explanations.  When accessing the menus, you will see
submenus on most of the items.  On the Attributes, for example, there
are three subitems.

Set	  - To set a specific number for strength.
Max Legal - To set the maximum legal value.
Maximum	  - To set the maximum value.

     Now, there may be a problem in translation here - when I say maximum, I
actually mean the maximum the game (Bards Tale) will display without showing
asterisks.
     All the menu options follow the same general format.  When you try to
set one of the data items, an input prompt will appear at the bottom of the
screen.  You cannot enter a number higher than the highest number shown.

****************
NOTE:
 At the number prompt, to enter zero, hit RETURN without typing anything.
****************

     When you modify your possessions, a prompt will appear at the bottom
of the screen telling you what to do.  After you have chosen an item, you
will be asked if you want to equip that item.  Answer with a 'Y' or 'N',
then press RETURN.

-------------------------------------------------------------------------
CAVEATS:
     If you equip an item on a character that can't normally use that item,
once you have started the game the only way to unequip it is to sell it,
trade it or drop it.  You will not even be given the Unequip option.

     Your modified character will NOT be saved unless you specifically do
so.  I consider this a safety feature rather than any real bother.

